FBIS3-47115 "dreas006_m_94002" FBIS-EAS-94-006 Document Type:Daily Report 10 Jan 1994 Thailand Defense Minister Receives Cambodian Counterpart BK1001143494 Bangkok Army Television Channel 5 in Thai 1200 GMT 10 Jan 94 BK1001143494 Bangkok Army Television Channel 5 Language: Thai Article Type:BFN [Text] General Tea Chamrat, deputy defense minister of Cambodia [title as heard], called on Defense Minister General Wichit Sukmak at the Defense Ministry this morning. After the meeting, Wichit told reporters that they had discussed Cambodia's request for Thai assistance in national development. In particular, Cambodia wants Thai soldiers to provide agricultural training and assistance with military uniforms. The two sides also discussed security along the border. The two sides agreed to cooperate in maintaining peace along the border.
